videos.headline: SDSU's Lamont Butler finishes strong for and-1 basket
videos.description: Lamont Butler converts at the rim through contact to score early for San Diego State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (SDSU's Lamont Butler finishes strong for and-1 basket) 2022/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anthony Black glides to the rim for an Arkansas dunk
videos.description: Davonte Davis passes ahead to Anthony Black for an emphatic jam in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony Black glides to the rim for an Arkansas dunk) 2022/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Council throws down reverse jam for Arkansas
videos.description: Ricky Council IV does it all for Arkansas with a steal on defense leading to an impressive finish in transition.

videos.headline: Keshad Johnson's emphatic slam beats shot clock for SDSU
videos.description: San Diego State's Darrion Trammell dishes to Keshad Johnson for a dunk against Arkansas.

videos.headline: Matt Bradley's nifty reverse puts San Diego State ahead late

videos.headline: Arkansas scores buzzer-beating tip-in to force OT

videos.headline: Arkansas gets crucial defensive stop to seal OT win vs. SDSU
videos.description: Arkansas hangs on to defeat San Diego State as Matt Bradley's late layup attempt rims out.
